<p><strong>原始套接字编程</strong></p>
<p>原始套接字编程主要是涉及到packet，这里给出packet的man文件：</p>
<p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="http://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man7/packet.7.html">PACKET</a></p>
<hr>
